le preventing its rotation in the opposite direction. The linkage units are spaced apart from each other and are connected by a pivot bar (<b>30</b>) connected at its ends to the ratchet arrangement of each linkage unit and actuatable by a lever (<b>31</b>) for overriding the rotation preventing action of the ratchet mechanism to allow the second arm to rotate freely.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>